<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Sage Hill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Home to a massive variety of both single-family and multiple-family residential units, the Sage Hills Real Estate offers future residents the options of the more luxurious bungalows with front-attached garages and large backyard ponds! The average cost of single-family detached homes for sale in Sage Hill is around $700,000, with the prices climbing as high as $3,300,000 for the more upscale properties.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The picturesque neighborhood is bound by the <a href="/nolan-hill.php">Nolan Hill</a> community on the west, the <a href="/kincora.php">Kincora</a> community on the south, the <a href="/evanston.php">Evanston</a> community on the east and the 144 Avenue NW on the north.</p>
        </div>
